  Definition of State  
    Definition of State 

    The state of an object encompasses all of the (usually static) properties of the object plus the current (usually dynamic) values of each of these properties  Hadar  Talking, Pacing, Smiling, Hungry, Tired    Peyman  Sitting, Listening, Typing, Hungry, Tired, Bored    My Bank Account  #123456, Checking, Open/Active, Overdrawn, Balance -1234.56    My Car  Jeep, Cherokee, 1992, White, 5-speed, paid-for, Stalled       
 
   

